    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4 text-green-100">
      <p><strong class="text-white">Odd/even schedule:</strong> Your watering days depend on your house number — even addresses get Tue/Thu/Sat, odd addresses get Wed/Fri/Sun. We program accordingly.</p>
      <p><strong class="text-white">Monday blackout.</strong> Nobody waters on Monday. Our controllers skip it automatically.</p>
      <p><strong class="text-white">Summer midday ban:</strong> From April through September, irrigation can't run between 10 a.m. and 6 p.m. We set run times for early morning only.</p>
      <p><strong class="text-white">Species sourcing:</strong> Most of our plant selections come from proven performers at the <a href="https://lascruces.gov/property/utilities/utility-services/water-conservation/" rel="noopener" target="_blank" class="text-green-300 hover:underline">Las Cruces water conservation demonstration garden on Motel Boulevard</a>.</p>
